The Itinerary
July 17 - fly from New York to Dublin; tour southwest Ireland by car;
July 20 - fly from Shannon Airport to Amsterdam;
July 22 - train from Amsterdam to Frankfurt, Germany; meet Louise and Marilyn; by car, south through Black Forest to Switzerland; tour Switzerland by car for one week;
July 29 - leave Louise and Marolyn; train to Paris;
Aug. 1 - fly from Paris to London;
Aug. 4 - fly London to Edinburgh;

